{"title":"Work Order","url":"https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/desk/work-order","summary":"This is the Work Order list view in the ERPNext Manufacturing module for SysMayal. The page displays 18 active work orders for manufacturing aloe vera-based products (INNOVALOE brand). Work orders include various products such as Aloe Vera Gel Spray Dried Powder, Aloe Vera Gel Juice, Aloe Vera Gel Concentrate, and Organic Inner Leaf Aloe Vera Powder. The list shows work order IDs (ranging from MFG-WO-00925 to MFG-WO-04226), manufacturing quantities (from 1 to 18,000 units), BOM (Bill of Materials) references, plant codes, and status (Not Started or Start). Some work orders are linked to specific sales orders. The system also displays failed email notification alerts related to workflow actions on TDS Product Specifications and COA (Certificate of Analysis) documents.","key_points":["Page displays 18 Work Orders in the Manufacturing module of ERPNext","Products being manufactured are aloe vera-based items under the INNOVALOE brand","Work order statuses include Not Started and Start","Manufacturing quantities range from 1 to 18,000 units","Work orders reference various BOMs (Bill of Materials) such as BOM-0334-001, BOM-0433-001, BOM-0705-LWpH-001","Plant codes displayed include 1M, 3W, 5M, 6M, 1D representing different production facilities","Some work orders are linked to sales orders like SO-02725-LORAND LABS LLC and SO-117326-AGROMAYAL BOTANICA","Failed email notifications present related to Workflow Actions on TDS Product Specifications and COA documents","Navigation includes Manufacturing Dashboard, BOM, Job Card, Stock Entry, and Production Planning modules","Available actions on work orders include Start, Copy to Clipboard, Export, Assign To, Print","Filters available include Item To Manufacture, Status, Plant Code, BOM No, Company, and dates"],"relevant_links":["https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/desk/dashboard-view/Manufacturing","https://erp.sysmayal2.cloud/desk/bom","https://erp.s